  <title translate="true">Goto_area_style</title>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The area style is used:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="3" colcount="2" style="width:100%; cell-padding:2px; cell-spacing:1px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:20px;">
          <para styleclass="TableText"><text style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">•</text></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">to draw area features in a GOTO action with a mapping where &quot;Use?&quot; is true.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:20px;">
          <para styleclass="TableText"><text style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">•</text></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">to draw the rectangle representing the value when a raster type symbol has a value selector.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:20px;">
          <para styleclass="TableText"><text style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:9pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">•</text></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="TableText"><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">to draw the background of a byte sized grid type symbol.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="TableText"><br/><image src="psyms_clip0073.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="TableText"><br/><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">To edit the area style, double click the property goto_area_style in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="psyms_Picture-Symbol-Properties" styleclass="TableText" translate="true">Symbol Property List</link><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Result sign" translate="true">» </text><text styleclass="TableText" translate="true">The style attributes are shown:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="TableText"><image src="psyms_clip0074.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="TableText"></para>
  </body>
